        <div class="row-dotted-line"></div>

        <h3>1. Get to the chrome web store</h3>
        
        <div class="ul-box">
            <ul>
                <li>Launch the chrome browser, if you're viewing this website through chrome press ctrl+t to open a new tab.</li>
                <li>On the new tab there will be an extensions shortcut you'll want to click it.</li>
                <li><strong>If</strong> your tab doesn't include the extensions shortcut <a href>Click here</a> for alternative way to get to extensions.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

